Titolo: Insurgency (video game)

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Insurgency is a multiplayer tactical first-person shooter video game developed and published by New World Interactive. It is a standalone sequel to Insurgency: Modern Infantry Combat, a community made mod for Valve's Source engine. The game was released for Microsoft Windows, OS X, and Linux on January 22, 2014.
The game received mixed to positive reviews from game critics, who compared it to Counter-Strike: Global Offensive, but was acclaimed by players for its realism, harsh difficulty, mod support, sound design, animations, levels and gameplay, and was equally praised for its optimization. The game's success spawned a spinoff, Day of Infamy, and a sequel, Insurgency: Sandstorm.

Genere: First-person shooter

Valutazione: N/A
